---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="The Project" description="Wyoming Coal-to-Ammonia Initiative - Next-generation industrial manufacturing with full carbon integration.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-800 to-primary-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 md:py-28">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight">
        Wyoming Coal-to-Ammonia Initiative
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-2xl">
        Next-generation industrial manufacturing with full carbon integration.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Project Overview -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Project Overview</h2>
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          CapStone's marquee initiative is a Coal-to-Ammonia project sited in Wyoming — a next-generation industrial facility converting regional coal resources into blue ammonia and dispatchable power generation, while integrating carbon capture and geological storage.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
          The project utilizes 21st-century gasification processes to produce low-carbon intensity ammonia at scale.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why This Matters -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-12 text-center">Why This Matters</h2>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <!-- National Security -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">National Security</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            Domestic ammonia production reduces reliance on foreign supply chains for a critical industrial input.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Food Supply Chain -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-accent-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-accent-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 6l3 1m0 0l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M6 7l3 9M6 7l6-2m6 2l3-1m-3 1l-3 9a5.002 5.002 0 006.001 0M18 7l3 9m-3-9l-6-2m0-2v2m0 16V5m0 16H9m3 0h3" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Food Supply Chain</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            Approximately 80% of global ammonia production supports agricultural fertilizer. Stable domestic supply protects American food security.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Clean Energy Transition -->
        <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-slate-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-slate-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-3">Clean Energy Transition</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600">
            Blue ammonia is emerging as a carbon-free fuel source. Demand is projected to grow significantly in the coming decade.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Project Status -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8">Project Status</h2>
      <div class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-200 rounded-xl p-8">
        <p class="text-lg text-slate-700 leading-relaxed">
          The project is currently in structured Pre-FEED development, leveraging Wyoming's emerging CO&#8322; storage regulatory framework and existing industrial fertilizer infrastructure.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Wyoming -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-slate-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8">Why Wyoming</h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-slate-300 leading-relaxed">
        Wyoming offers a unique combination of abundant coal resources, established industrial infrastructure, and regulatory leadership in carbon storage — making it the ideal location for next-generation energy manufacturing.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section -->
  <section class="py-20 bg-primary-900 text-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold">Interested in partnership opportunities?</h2>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="inline-flex items-center px-8 py-3 bg-white text-primary-900 font-medium rounded-lg hover:bg-slate-100 transition-colors"
        >
          Contact Us
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
